Mehtods:
A method block of code that contains instructions which are executed
when the method is called
Why should we create methods?
1)they allow us to reuse code.
2)save time
3)save memory
4)code is more organized
5)code changing becomes easier (only have to do it in one place)

When should we create a method?
if we are repeating more than 3 lines of code twice then we should create a method

Syntax of a method:
returnType methodName(){

}

example
void printHello(){
sout"Hello";
}